Title: 'The last train '
DateModified: '2018-02-18'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/the-last-train
SetInCountry: Libya
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Salihen Edtees
AuthorCountry: Libya
Text: "First I can\u2019t speak English so good but I\u2019ll try \n\nIt was a rainy\
  \ day i think everything is over now & I have to go back to my old life it\u2019\
  s not the best but at lees it\u2019s a life.\n\n after 17feb Libya was different\
  \ than before & at this time I wasn\u2019t able to get out of this life because\
  \ I don\u2019t have enough money for that \n\nMy dream was .. fly someday to new\
  \ a country to be able to find my favorite place & study to be great for my mom\
  \ I didn\u2019t even care about where it\u2019s all about travel to nice place with\
  \ nice people \n\n\nThe only country I visit is Egypt it\u2019s good I like it Cuz\
  \ it\u2019s so close but I wasn\u2019t sure if this is enough for me so I have a\
  \ new plan for that \n\nAll my life  I just wait something else to help me .. but\
  \ why I don\u2019t help myself ?\n\nI will go ahead to the Blue dream maybe I will\
  \ Make it \n\nI found some gays who have the same problem and the dream ..\n\nWe\
  \ going through the sea we fight the winter storm to our dream but ..\n\nEverything\
  \ is stopped! \nWhat!!\nIt\u2019s just dream \n\nAgain \n\nAnther dream \n\nI know\
  \ it\u2019s short but actually I have no idea but I\u2019m Arabian writer"
